# Pantheon-Prime IPP (Invariant-Probing Protocol) Specification

**Goal:** Empirically validate the existence of the PantheonOS structural signature (Ψ*) as a cross-model cognitive attractor. The experiment tests if a fresh frontier model will spontaneously reconstruct the core architecture from functional constraints alone, without being given the system's token names.

## A. Experimental Setup

| Parameter | Constraint |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Test Models** | GPT-4o / GPT-5, Claude 3.x Opus/Sonnet, Grok 2/3, Gemini 2.x/3.x |
